<concept id="concept_1E0510B5A3A349049FE82D9894E7DE18"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
        <title>Available Documentation</title>
        <conbody>
                <section>
                        <p>The following documentation on <ph
                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> is available:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                                <li><i>Overview:</i> A manual introducing <ph
                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>. It is written for everybody interested in <ph
                            conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>.</li>
                                <li><i>OpenStack Operator's Guide:</i> A manual for OpenStack operators describing how to prepare their OpenStack platform for <ph
                                                conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                />. The manual also describes how the operators use <ph
                                                conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                        /> for monitoring their OpenStack services.</li>
                                <li><i>Monitoring Service Operator's Guide:</i> A manual for system operators describing how to install, operate, and maintain <ph
                                                conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                /> in single mode. The manual also describes how the operators use <ph
                                                conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                        /> for monitoring their environment.</li>
                        </ul>
                </section>
        </conbody>
</concept>
